java.lang.Object
org.newsclub.net.unix.tipc.AFTIPCTopologyEvent
@NonNullByDefault public final class AFTIPCTopologyEvent extends Object
A TIPC topology event received by the AFTIPCTopologyWatcher as a result of an AFTIPCTopologySubscription.

    • getLinkName

      public @Nullable String getLinkName() throws IOException
      Returns the link name for a link state event requested by AFTIPCTopologySubscription.TIPC_LINK_STATE or AFTIPCTopologyWatcher.addLinkStateSubscription(). A link name is something like "f875a40e707d:eth0-8c1645f2ce27:eth0"
      Returns:
      The link name, or null if unsupported.
      Throws:
      IOException - on error.
